msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:175"
msgid "`v0.5.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.5.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:177
msgid ""
"`ptool.ask.confirm(prompt[, options])` asks the user for a yes/no answer."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.ask.confirm(prompt[, options])` solicita ao usuário uma resposta de "
"sim/não."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:179
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:179"
msgid "`prompt` (string, required): The prompt shown to the user."
