#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:194
msgid "ptool.ask.select"
msgstr "ptool.ask.select"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:196
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:196"
msgid "`v0.5.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.5.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:198
msgid ""
"`ptool.ask.select(prompt, items[, options])` asks the user to choose one "
"item from a list."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.ask.select(prompt, items[, options])` solicita ao usuário que escolha "
"um item de uma lista."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:201
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:201"
msgid "`prompt` (string, required): The prompt shown to the user."
msgstr "`prompt` (string, obrigatório): O prompt mostrado ao usuário."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:202
msgid "`items` (table, required): Candidate items. Each entry may be:"
msgstr "`items` (table, obrigatório): Itens candidatos. Cada entrada pode ser:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:202
msgid ""
"A string, which is used as both the display label and the returned value."
msgstr "Um string, usado tanto como rótulo exibido quanto como valor retornado."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:202
msgid "A table like `{ label = \"Patch\", value = \"patch\" }`."
msgstr "Um table como `{ label = \"Patch\", value = \"patch\" }`."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:205
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:205"
msgid "`options` (table, optional): Prompt options. Supported fields:"
msgstr "`options` (table, opcional): Opções do prompt. Campos suportados:"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:205
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:205"
msgid "`help` (string, optional): Extra help text shown below the prompt."
msgstr ""
"`help` (string, opcional): Texto de ajuda extra exibido abaixo do prompt."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:205
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:205"
